1
00:01:05,200 --> 00:01:06,160
Shen Lingbo.

2
00:01:07,640 --> 00:01:10,200
Prince Bulei, are you looking for me?

3
00:01:10,200 --> 00:01:12,840
Why was my cavalry ambushed by the Bai Army?

4
00:01:12,840 --> 00:01:13,880
The only person who knew the marching route

5
00:01:13,880 --> 00:01:15,200
was you.

6
00:01:15,200 --> 00:01:16,130
How would I know?

7
00:01:16,480 --> 00:01:17,880
Your discipline is lax,

8
00:01:17,880 --> 00:01:19,080
you exposed your tracks,

9
00:01:19,080 --> 00:01:20,740
and you don't blame yourself?

10
00:01:22,480 --> 00:01:24,280
Do you think I won't kill you?

11
00:01:25,560 --> 00:01:26,920
What are you laughing at?

12
00:01:26,920 --> 00:01:29,720
Does Prince Bulei only know how to bully women?

13
00:01:34,080 --> 00:01:35,320
Shen Lingbo.

14
00:01:35,320 --> 00:01:37,560
I have never loved a woman in my life.

15
00:01:38,200 --> 00:01:39,280
You are the first.

16
00:01:39,680 --> 00:01:40,600
So what?

17
00:01:41,080 --> 00:01:42,000
You fool.

18
00:01:48,280 --> 00:01:49,560
I love you so much.

19
00:01:49,920 --> 00:01:52,200
You... You dare to kill me?

20
00:01:52,240 --> 00:01:53,700
Who cares about your love?

21
00:01:53,920 --> 00:01:55,039
You're crazy.

22
00:01:57,039 --> 00:01:58,640
A man who looks down on women

23
00:01:59,039 --> 00:02:01,440
doesn't deserve to leave this place alive.

24
00:02:11,080 --> 00:02:13,600
It looks like you need help.

25
00:02:15,720 --> 00:02:18,600
Royal Brother told you long ago,

26
00:02:18,800 --> 00:02:20,720
the Lingbo flower is poisonous.

27
00:02:20,720 --> 00:02:22,400
You betrayed me.

28
00:02:25,280 --> 00:02:26,800
You are nothing but a dog.

29
00:02:27,240 --> 00:02:29,640
And yet you covet your master's position.

30
00:02:38,400 --> 00:02:39,600
Perfect timing.

31
00:02:39,800 --> 00:02:41,079
You were too slow.

32
00:02:48,400 --> 00:02:51,040
Who will be next?

33
00:02:51,720 --> 00:02:54,079
Ruyu, get rid of the body.

34
00:03:15,080 --> 00:03:16,680
In the Marquis of Loyalty and Justice Manor,

35
00:03:16,680 --> 00:03:18,560
is there no one even to pour tea?

36
00:03:22,600 --> 00:03:25,060
The good tea in the Marquis Manor has run out.

37
00:03:25,240 --> 00:03:26,970
Please bear with it, Miss Shen.

38
00:03:27,000 --> 00:03:28,730
Is the Marquis Manor this poor?

39
00:03:29,560 --> 00:03:31,480
Naturally, we cannot compare to the Shen Residence.

40
00:03:31,480 --> 00:03:35,840
I wonder if you are here to cause trouble or handle business, Miss Shen.

41
00:03:36,240 --> 00:03:37,600
Manchuan told me

42
00:03:38,079 --> 00:03:40,140
to treat the Marquis Manor as my home.

43
00:03:40,760 --> 00:03:42,280
I have always remembered those words.

44
00:03:42,280 --> 00:03:43,920
Now that my father has passed away,

45
00:03:43,920 --> 00:03:45,800
the Prime Minister's Manor is desolate.

46
00:03:45,800 --> 00:03:48,440
As a woman, I am truly afraid.

47
00:03:48,560 --> 00:03:52,400
So you mean to live in the Marquis Manor, Miss Shen?

48
00:03:52,400 --> 00:03:54,079
You are unmarried, Miss Shen.

49
00:03:54,240 --> 00:03:57,440
Living here might attract gossip, won't it?

50
00:03:57,560 --> 00:03:59,360
Is it your place to speak here?

51
00:03:59,360 --> 00:03:59,800
You...

52
00:04:04,080 --> 00:04:07,160
Song Xuan, you should have some self-awareness.

53
00:04:07,800 --> 00:04:09,730
What do you mean by that, Miss Shen?

54
00:04:10,080 --> 00:04:14,120
It is time you gave up the position of mistress of the Marquis Manor.

55
00:04:14,840 --> 00:04:16,570
Does Manchuan know about this?

56
00:04:17,040 --> 00:04:18,160
So what if he knows?

57
00:04:18,680 --> 00:04:19,880
So what if he doesn't?

58
00:04:25,400 --> 00:04:27,080
He and I are old acquaintances.

59
00:04:27,080 --> 00:04:28,880
We share a bond of life and death.

60
00:04:29,080 --> 00:04:30,800
The bond between us

61
00:04:31,720 --> 00:04:34,240
is not something a latecomer like you can interfere with.

62
00:04:34,240 --> 00:04:35,570
Have you asked Manchuan

63
00:04:35,920 --> 00:04:38,000
if he wants you by his side?

64
00:04:38,159 --> 00:04:40,290
He is just temporarily blinded by you.

65
00:04:40,400 --> 00:04:41,520
Once you are gone,

66
00:04:42,080 --> 00:04:44,240
I have my ways to make him come back to me.

67
00:04:44,240 --> 00:04:47,120
Trying to seize a position using past friendship?

68
00:04:47,400 --> 00:04:49,600
You are being too impatient, Miss Shen.

69
00:04:49,600 --> 00:04:50,440
Other than me,

70
00:04:51,400 --> 00:04:53,460
no one can protect the Marquis Manor.

71
00:04:53,920 --> 00:04:55,720
You are too arrogant, Miss Shen.

72
00:04:56,680 --> 00:04:58,740
Then you just wait and see, Miss Song.

73
00:05:00,800 --> 00:05:01,400
Manchuan.

74
00:05:03,440 --> 00:05:05,240
Daylily, are you alright?

75
00:05:07,800 --> 00:05:09,130
What are you doing here?

76
00:05:09,720 --> 00:05:12,200
Didn't you say I could treat this place as my home?

77
00:05:12,200 --> 00:05:14,440
That was before I got married.

78
00:05:15,080 --> 00:05:16,410
So it doesn't count now?

79
00:05:16,760 --> 00:05:19,120
Now I have to listen to my wife.

80
00:05:19,640 --> 00:05:23,000
After all, she is the mistress of Zhongyi Manor.

81
00:05:23,400 --> 00:05:25,400
What kind of spell has she put on you?

82
00:05:25,600 --> 00:05:27,640
I know my own heart now.

83
00:05:28,760 --> 00:05:30,620
It's time you realized yours too.

84
00:05:34,400 --> 00:05:36,760
Song Xuan, you're quite the schemer.

85
00:05:46,000 --> 00:05:47,200
I've made you suffer.

86
00:05:49,320 --> 00:05:50,159
Manchuan.

87
00:05:51,040 --> 00:05:53,100
Have you ever regretted marrying me?

88
00:05:53,200 --> 00:05:56,000
Marrying you was the best decision of my life.

89
00:05:58,080 --> 00:06:00,120
Where could the Song Army squad be?

90
00:06:01,680 --> 00:06:03,440
We can't wait any longer.

91
00:06:03,880 --> 00:06:05,480
Are you talking about the Academy case?

92
00:06:05,480 --> 00:06:08,010
The rumors out there are going to crush Chuyi.

93
00:06:08,120 --> 00:06:08,840
Go on.

94
00:06:09,360 --> 00:06:10,440
The Bai family has a daughter,

95
00:06:10,440 --> 00:06:11,700
who looks like a beast,

96
00:06:11,720 --> 00:06:12,680
kills people,

97
00:06:12,840 --> 00:06:14,370
and is utterly terrifying.

98
00:06:14,400 --> 00:06:16,400
This is practically becoming a folktale.

99
00:06:16,400 --> 00:06:17,330
What's worse is,

100
00:06:17,680 --> 00:06:19,040
Chuyi is unconscious at times,

101
00:06:19,040 --> 00:06:20,170
and lucid at others.

102
00:06:20,480 --> 00:06:22,740
She can't come forward to clear her name.

103
00:06:23,880 --> 00:06:24,560
These rumors

104
00:06:24,560 --> 00:06:26,960
were all spread by Ji Ruyu and Tuoya.

105
00:06:27,080 --> 00:06:29,000
Their goal is to provoke Chuyi.

106
00:06:29,280 --> 00:06:32,040
I've told everyone in the manor to keep it from Chuyi.

107
00:06:32,040 --> 00:06:34,880
So our top priority is to solve the case as soon as possible.

108
00:06:34,880 --> 00:06:38,320
But didn't you say Ji Ruyu and Tuoya acted cleanly,

109
00:06:38,560 --> 00:06:40,080
and left no clues?

110
00:06:42,240 --> 00:06:43,280
There is a way.

111
00:06:43,920 --> 00:06:46,000
If we back them into a corner,

112
00:06:46,240 --> 00:06:47,840
they'll eventually slip up.

113
00:06:48,000 --> 00:06:48,560
Wait.

114
00:06:49,240 --> 00:06:50,240
I have a good idea.

115
00:06:50,800 --> 00:06:51,600
What is it?

116
00:06:56,840 --> 00:06:58,000
Big or Small?

117
00:06:58,320 --> 00:06:59,760
No more bets.

118
00:07:00,320 --> 00:07:01,280
I bet...

119
00:07:07,680 --> 00:07:08,280
It's over.

120
00:07:09,400 --> 00:07:10,240
It's all gone.

121
00:07:10,280 --> 00:07:12,810
You still owe me one thousand taels of silver.

122
00:07:12,880 --> 00:07:13,810
How will you pay?

123
00:07:13,920 --> 00:07:16,040
I can't afford that much silver.

124
00:07:17,120 --> 00:07:18,720
If you don't have the silver,

125
00:07:18,920 --> 00:07:20,450
stay here and be my servant.

126
00:07:22,240 --> 00:07:22,960
Wait, wait.

127
00:07:23,400 --> 00:07:25,130
Can I trade information for it?

128
00:07:25,720 --> 00:07:28,040
What news of yours is worth a thousand taels?

129
00:07:28,040 --> 00:07:29,800
Do you think I'm running a charity?

130
00:07:29,800 --> 00:07:30,280
No.

131
00:07:38,920 --> 00:07:40,000
Let's hear it.

132
00:07:40,880 --> 00:07:44,010
You know about the murder at the Capital Academy, right?

133
00:07:44,480 --> 00:07:46,409
Our Zhongyi Manor has found a clue.

134
00:07:46,840 --> 00:07:48,040
What clue?

135
00:07:48,920 --> 00:07:51,720
Just tell me if this news is worth a thousand taels.

136
00:07:54,440 --> 00:07:55,159
Deal.

137
00:07:56,480 --> 00:07:57,680
Our Young Madam...

138
00:07:58,240 --> 00:07:59,400
found a woodcutter.

139
00:08:00,200 --> 00:08:03,060
He claims to be an eyewitness to the Academy murder.

140
00:08:04,280 --> 00:08:07,680
The woodcutter said the killer was a woman.

141
00:08:12,240 --> 00:08:14,200
Didn't you say you found the murderer?

142
00:08:14,200 --> 00:08:14,930
Where is she?

143
00:08:16,400 --> 00:08:17,560
It's not you, is it?

144
00:08:18,080 --> 00:08:18,920
Be patient.

145
00:08:19,320 --> 00:08:20,360
She's on her way.

146
00:08:32,559 --> 00:08:33,240
Boss Ji,

147
00:08:33,559 --> 00:08:35,919
coming to Zhongyi Manor in the middle of the night,

148
00:08:35,919 --> 00:08:37,159
why cover your face?

149
00:08:40,480 --> 00:08:41,610
It really is Ji Ruyu.

150
00:08:44,159 --> 00:08:45,720
I miscalculated.

151
00:08:45,800 --> 00:08:48,080
Do with me what you will.

152
00:08:56,400 --> 00:08:58,660
I didn't expect the culprit to be Ji Ruyu.

153
00:08:58,680 --> 00:08:59,610
So, what's next?

154
00:08:59,840 --> 00:09:01,400
Although I don't like your Bai family,

155
00:09:01,400 --> 00:09:02,640
in matters like this,

156
00:09:02,800 --> 00:09:04,800
I will enforce the law impartially.

157
00:09:04,920 --> 00:09:06,880
You'd better keep your word.

158
00:09:08,080 --> 00:09:08,680
My Lord.

159
00:09:10,000 --> 00:09:11,600
I want to have a word with you.

160
00:09:16,720 --> 00:09:18,920
I didn't expect you to be so naive, Boss Ji.

161
00:09:18,920 --> 00:09:21,080
You walk right into any trap set for you.

162
00:09:21,080 --> 00:09:23,120
If I hadn't noticed something was wrong in time,

163
00:09:23,120 --> 00:09:24,720
and had Sangbiao follow you,

164
00:09:25,840 --> 00:09:28,570
you probably wouldn't have made it back tonight.

165
00:09:29,240 --> 00:09:30,840
Hurry up and thank Miss Shen.

166
00:09:31,120 --> 00:09:32,320
Thank you, Miss Shen.

167
00:09:32,480 --> 00:09:35,480
Next time, please use your brain before you act.

168
00:09:38,120 --> 00:09:39,850
I was played by Song Xuan today.

169
00:09:40,080 --> 00:09:42,160
I will definitely settle this score.

170
00:09:42,400 --> 00:09:44,280
What do you intend to do, Princess?

171
00:09:44,280 --> 00:09:46,410
Are you going to walk into a trap again?

172
00:09:46,600 --> 00:09:48,280
There is an old saying in the Central Plains.

173
00:09:48,280 --> 00:09:50,800
Give her a taste of her own medicine.

174
00:09:51,800 --> 00:09:53,060
What are you planning?

175
00:09:53,200 --> 00:09:55,880
It is time to use the missing Song Army.

176
00:09:56,760 --> 00:09:58,490
Then I'll await your good news.

177
00:09:59,000 --> 00:10:01,200
As soon as Song Xuan leaves the Capital,

178
00:10:01,240 --> 00:10:03,800
the entire Capital will be at our mercy.

179
00:10:04,920 --> 00:10:06,040
I hope so.

180
00:10:14,480 --> 00:10:15,680
It is all my fault.

181
00:10:16,040 --> 00:10:17,040
I don't blame you.

182
00:10:17,560 --> 00:10:18,880
I didn't expect

183
00:10:18,920 --> 00:10:21,480
Song Xuan to use such dirty tricks.

184
00:10:21,760 --> 00:10:23,080
But that Shen Lingbo,

185
00:10:23,720 --> 00:10:25,380
she knew clearly it was a trap,

186
00:10:25,600 --> 00:10:27,280
yet she only had her guard follow me,

187
00:10:27,280 --> 00:10:28,610
instead of stopping me.

188
00:10:28,840 --> 00:10:30,160
She is warning me.

189
00:10:30,640 --> 00:10:33,920
Set fire to this gambling house later.

190
00:10:37,080 --> 00:10:39,280
Princess, we built this gambling house...

191
00:10:39,280 --> 00:10:40,440
Say no more.

192
00:10:40,920 --> 00:10:42,680
This place has been compromised.

193
00:10:42,680 --> 00:10:45,280
This is the only way I can protect you.

194
00:10:47,840 --> 00:10:49,120
It is all my fault.

195
00:10:49,560 --> 00:10:54,240
Burn it. That way, they'll think we're panicking.

196
00:10:58,680 --> 00:11:00,080
But what about Bai Chuyi?

197
00:11:01,080 --> 00:11:02,810
Are we just going to let her off?

198
00:11:03,400 --> 00:11:05,920
I have full control over her dreams.

199
00:11:06,920 --> 00:11:08,560
She won't last much longer.
